user_prompt: Under the dark lights, two friends sit side by side in a PC room and are immersed in a simulation game. The keyboard and mouse are constantly ringing with fast and sharp typing and clicks. Complex game screens are quickly switched on the monitor, and the two people's hands are busy on the keyboard, almost invisible.
prompt_variant: Under the glow of dark lights, two friends are absorbed in a fast-paced simulation game, their hands a blur on the keyboard and mouse.
